### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@jobId = 1

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###
### Iniciar un nuevo job de scraping
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://extend.emarsys.com/products/recommended",
  "username": "usuario@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "maxProducts": 50,
  "timeout": 30000,
  "headless": true,
  "useCache": true
}

###
### Iniciar scraping sin credenciales (usando las del .env)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxProducts": 100,
  "headless": true
}

###
### Obtener estado de un job específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/jobs/{{jobId}}

###
### Listar todos los jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/jobs

###
### Obtener estadísticas de la cola
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/stats

###
### Reintentar un job fallido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/jobs/{{jobId}}/retry

###
### Cancelar un job
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/jobs/{{jobId}}

###
### Limpiar jobs completados y fallidos
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/jobs/completed/clear

###
### Ver documentación Swagger
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docs
